{"tid":1959272,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"湯文亮 唔該你執返個CV 唔好再呃讀者","createTime":"2020-04-05T09:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T04:14:38.000Z","uid":54373,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7e6361724ae9b8390b1c2710161fb04f945aa957","tid":1959272,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:37:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">入福布斯叫-廖湯慧靄 而唔係你條垃圾</span><br />\n<br />\n但你完全唔提，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你只係紀慧集團入面一個員工！</span>有種就同全香港人講，紀慧集團係你？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔通我做百佳，我出本書話自己N年前已打進福布斯香港富豪榜第一位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作者簡介：<br />\n<br />\n湯文亮博士<br />\n紀惠集團行政總裁，資深地產投資者，縱橫樓市30多年，集團在本港持有物業市值總值達數百億元，<span style=\"color: red;\">並在2017年開始打進《福布斯》香港富豪排行榜，2019年最新排名第25位。</span> 同時也是活躍的專欄作家，在財經雜誌《Money Monday》、《i-money智富雜誌》、《明報》及《蘋果日報》等均有其專欄。由2011年開始在「Yahoo! 地產」撰寫Blog，點擊率超過2億人次，現於「<a href=\"http://m.property.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.property.hk&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfzy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=e16271ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">m.property.hk</a>」、「NOW地產」、「PropNew潮流主場」及「橙」都有撰寫文章。湯博士在澳門出生及長大，後赴加拿大留學，曾獲第13屆傑出華人獎，並先後出版《辣招如何扭曲樓市》、《破解樓市之謎》等10本暢銷書籍。"},{"pid":"68b422b5cf6b2d0bd04dc517aa827cca96bb19a4","tid":1959272,"uid":28765,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"自我介紹都係虛構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a548cb3a2ffc85e1d5615ea5be80da4508f82d98","tid":1959272,"uid":89546,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係好撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但報紙佬仲好鍾意搵佢鳩UP"},{"pid":"fa5fb95b947e4ddf7974f099003eb6c387bf7ebb","tid":1959272,"u