其專欄。由2011年開始在「Yahoo! 地產」撰寫Blog，點擊率超過2億人次，現於「<a href=\"http://m.property.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.property.hk&d=4DrNtUYtvprXc3sGeUgfzy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=e16271ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">m.property.hk</a>」、「NOW地產」、「PropNew潮流主場」及「橙」都有撰寫文章。湯博士在澳門出生及長大，後赴加拿大留學，曾獲第13屆傑出華人獎，並先後出版《辣招如何扭曲樓市》、《破解樓市之謎》等10本暢銷書籍。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢個家姐</span></span></strong>廖太歷年出任不少公職，熱心服務社群，貢獻惠及香港各界，成就深得社會讚許。她曾榮獲香港特別行政區政府銅紫荊星章(BBS)及銀紫荊星章(SBS)，以及香港紅十字會熱心服務榮譽獎章。另外，她是加拿大多倫多大學的Arbor獎得主，並躋身亞洲版《福布斯》雜誌2018年香港富豪榜第25位。"},{"pid":"4334d777b471b0a6b455813dfba32823023c7544","tid":1959272,"uid":77626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68b422b5cf6b2d0bd04dc517aa827cca96bb19a4","tid":1959272,"uid":28765,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"自我介紹都係虛構<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:12:46.000Z","msg":"true"},{"pid":"2c00c8c9160f595fddff3529dc89593120d1acce","tid":1959272,"uid":44980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"裙腳仔嚟講佢算唔算最老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cdb571a46caeb060f1f302aa94979df2651f12","tid":1959272,"uid":117754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:21:14.000Z","msg":"好心佢喇, 男人老狗靠家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一陣又同家姐講連仔蝦佢.......有料既自己打片新天空喇. 下下都靠家姐個名. 香港男人佢都算無用."},{"pid":"76565653b1b429fc4959e12ce211610b06d3d4b7","tid":1959272,"uid":254114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:50:25.000Z","msg":"弟憑姊貴"},{"pid":"6f9526e06b7346b90b1984cef8dd35197adde269","tid":1959272,"uid":97846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b51acc03e4793589589fe5f79e7132dba2bb47a","tid":1959272,"uid":278264,"like":2,"dislike":0